Male adult (holotype, in lateral view) of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Song &amp; Qi" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Chironomidae" genus="Stenochironomus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Stenochironomus annulus" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulus">
