<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Male adult (holotype) of Stenochironomus annulus Song &amp; Qi sp. nov. A hypopygium in dorsal view B hypopygium in ventral view C superior volsella." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1104.81403.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/693997" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">5</figureCitation>
